Bulge info https://courseware.e-education.psu.edu/courses/earth540/Tides1.bulges.png

The tides in the seas are caused by the gravitational pull of the the Moon. When the Moon comes near to Earth, it can cause some sort of disturbances in the animals. They may act strangely or may have some neurological problems on the day when Moon comes nearer to the Earth.

